{"tid":1583352,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"教評會出左本洗腦同抹黑示威活動既小冊子","createTime":"2019-09-20T14:26:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-21T01:31:19.000Z","uid":61886,"like":5,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"dd52a373200603981e8f97a2ae35f97065a13c97","tid":1583352,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T14:26:23.000Z","msg":"先比幾頁大家睇下<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/htoPPJR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhtoPPJR.png&h=2a39eefc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1YprRXd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1YprRXd.png&h=322b5501&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OXpSNvz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOXpSNvz.png&h=97cb2118&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hTBazaA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhTBazaA.png&h=5cd2526c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xzUfLhk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxzUfLhk.png&h=83bb020f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n幾肯定依本野會比啲藍絲校長或者老師拎黎上德育課<br />\n<br />\n全小冊子下載<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.edconvergence.org.hk/pdf/booklet190830.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.edconvergence.org.hk%2Fpdf%2Fbooklet190830.pdf&d=2aT02SOmMwK2whwg3zZG14GitI067obQ02bu1xQE4oc%3D&h=04e45533\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.edconvergence.org.hk/pdf/booklet190830.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n教評會網址<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.edconvergence.org.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.edconvergence.org.hk&d=2aT02SOmMwK2whwg3zZG14GitI067obQ02bu1xQE4oc%3D&h=2576bc9e\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.edconvergence.org.hk</a><br />\n<br />\n請大家廣傳<br />\n堅拒抹黑 洗腦 偏頗既教材<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a036a8395d5767b5a11851517262e83775efd599","tid":1583352,"uid":61886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T14:27:10.000Z","msg":"延伸閱讀<br />\n<br />\nFrom wiki<br />\n教育評議會，簡稱：教評會，於1994年10月在香港成立，教評會由一群教育工作者所組成，是關注香港教育事務的團體，為香港教育政策提供建議。教評會認為香港特區的教育政策應主要由專業教育人員領導及參與，並應以正面、理性、積極、專業的態度與立場，推動教育改革，提高香港的教育質素。教評會支持香港議會回歸理性，共同為提升香港教育水平而努力。<br />\n<br />\nFrom 立場<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/society/教協-教聯和教評的-政治力量-角力/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%E6%95%99%E5%8D%94-%E6%95%99%E8%81%AF%E5%92%8C%E6%95%99%E8%A9%95%E7%9A%84-%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB%E5%8A%9B%E9%87%8F-%E8%A7%92%E5%8A%9B%2F&d=2aT02SOmMwK2whwg3zZG14GitI067obQ02bu1xQE4oc%3D&h=63c563ca\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%E6%95%99%E5%8D%94-%E6%95%99%E8%81%AF%E5%92%8C%E6%95%99%E8%A9%95%E7%9A%84-%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB%E5%8A%9B%E9%87%8F-%E8%A7%92%E5%8A%9B%2F&h=bb8c4464\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/society/教協-教聯和教評的-政治力量-角力/</a>"},{"pid":"38f789fc0d32064a3558e6cc83db7b9e7f6ef17c","tid":1583352,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T14:28:12.000Z","msg":"依單野唔係推唔到上熱門下話"},{"pid":"45c4b18b44aecf47390b05e6c924904cced65cfd","tid":1583352,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T14:28:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4205e48faba6ce4d9449ed4de52940ea389e606e","tid":1583352,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T14:29:09.000Z","msg":"推 1/10"},{"pid":"e817c6b0a377e25033e10537b2f2d52495e18156","tid":1583352,"uid":229920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T14:29:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b533f4618bb980983b56cd5c9c13370c37392d70","tid":1583352,"uid":115715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20